</head>
<body>

   

    <div class="recipe-container">
        <h1>🥗 Veg Fried Rice Recipe</h1>
       

        <h2>Ingredients:</h2>
        <ul class="ingredients-list">
            <li>2 cups Cooked Basmati Rice</li>
            <li>1 cup Mixed Vegetables (Carrots, Beans, Capsicum, Peas)</li>
            <li>2 tbsp Oil</li>
            <li>1 tbsp Chopped Garlic</li>
            <li>1 tbsp Chopped Spring Onions</li>
            <li>1 tbsp Soy Sauce</li>
            <li>½ tsp Vinegar</li>
            <li>½ tsp Black Pepper</li>
            <li>Salt to taste</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Instructions:</h2>
        <ol class="instructions-list">
            <li>Heat oil in a pan and sauté chopped garlic until golden.</li>
            <li>Add chopped vegetables and stir-fry on high heat for 2 minutes.</li>
            <li>Mix in soy sauce, vinegar, black pepper, and salt.</li>
            <li>Add cooked rice and toss everything together on high flame.</li>
            <li>Garnish with chopped spring onions and serve hot.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
